---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — RelayLaunch"
  description="RelayLaunch privacy policy. How we collect, use, and protect your personal information."
  canonicalUrl="https://relaylaunch.com/privacy/"
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 740px;">
      <h1 class="section-title" style="margin-bottom: 32px;">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="section-sub" style="margin-bottom: 40px;">Last updated: March 11, 2026</p>

      <div class="prose">
        <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>When you use our website or submit a form, we may collect:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Contact information</strong> — name, email address, business name</li>
          <li><strong>Form submissions</strong> — responses to our intake questionnaire and lead magnet forms</li>
          <li><strong>Usage data</strong> — pages visited, time on site, and referral source (via Google Analytics)</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Respond to your inquiries and provide our services</li>
          <li>Send you the resources you requested (e.g., the Complete Analysis checklist)</li>
          <li>Improve our website and services based on usage patterns</li>
          <li>Communicate about our services if you've opted in</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>We use the following third-party services:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Google Analytics 4</strong> — website analytics (anonymized IP)</li>
          <li><strong>Cloudflare</strong> — hosting and CDN</li>
          <li><strong>n8n</strong> — form submission processing (self-hosted)</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties.</p>

        <h2>Cookies</h2>
        <p>Our website uses minimal cookies for analytics and theme preferences. No advertising or tracking cookies are used.</p>

        <h2>Data Security</h2>
        <p>We implement industry-standard security measures including HTTPS encryption, secure hosting on Cloudflare, and limited access to personal data.</p>

        <h2>Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You may request to view, update, or delete your personal information at any time by contacting us at <a href="mailto:hello@relaylaunch.com">hello@relaylaunch.com</a>.</p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy, contact us at:</p>
        <p><strong>RelayLaunch LLC</strong><br />
        Watertown, MA<br />
        <a href="mailto:hello@relaylaunch.com">hello@relaylaunch.com</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose h2 {
    font-size: 22px;
    margin-top: 40px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
  .prose p {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    color: var(--color-muted);
  }
  .prose ul {
    list-style: disc;
    padding-left: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .prose li {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    color: var(--color-muted);
  }
  .prose strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
</style>
